  "prompt": "What is the \"Dale la vuelta a la tortilla!\" video all about?",
  "response": "\"Dale la vuelta a la tortilla!\" is a motivational campaign video by BBVA Spain. It showcases stories of resilience and overcoming adversity, with the goal of inspiring viewers to take control of their lives and turn difficulties into opportunities. The phrase \"Dale la vuelta a la tortilla\" translates to \"Turn the situation around,\" metaphorically encouraging people to change their perspective and improve their circumstances. The video often highlights personal and professional transformation, promoting optimism and proactive behaviour.",
